title: Star Wars - Republic Commando.rar
description:
System requirements:

- CPU: Pentium III or AMD Athlon 1.0 Ghz 
- 256 Mb RAM
- 64MB 3D Graphics card with Vertex Shader and Pixel Shader 1.1(VS/PS) capability required.
- OS: Windows 98SE/ME/2000/XP
- 2 GB of free hard disk space
- 100% DirectX 9.0c compatible Audio Device
- Microsoft DirectX 9.0c

Recommended machine claim:

- CPU: Pentium 4 2.0 GHz, or AMD Athlon XP 2400 2.0 GHz or faster CPU
- 512 Mb (Vista 1024 Mb) RAM
- 128MB 3D Graphics card with Vertex Shader and Pixel Shader 2.0(VS/PS) capability required.- Ati Radeon 9600 XT
- OS: Windows 98SE/ME/2000/XP
- 2 GB of free hard disk space
- 100% DirectX 9.0c compatible Audio Device
- Microsoft DirectX 9.0c

Teamwork, perseverance and tactical sense. This it what the game requests... :)
